Fig. 113
). Claw 5.2–6.4 times shorter than tibiotarsus.

Hind leg: precoxae and coxa with 1, 1, 3 setae (Fig. 93 ). Trochanter with anterior trochanteral organ, 3 anterior and 1 posterior setae; femur with 12 setae: 2 posterior ones are very small (
Fig. 116
